  "description": {
    "zh": "作为一个有多年经验的猎场看守人，我知道如果森林里有感染源的话，那你就一定得立刻把感染源从森林里移除从而防止整片森林都被感染。现在这里就有一个感染源，人们叫他Shturman，他和他的成员就驻扎在锯木厂里，这样一来我的自然保护区就危险了。解决他，为了森林和人们。记得保持警惕，Shturman有好几个同伴，他们也都是神枪手。",
    "en": "For many years working as a gamekeeper, I know that if there is an infection in the forest, then you need to get rid of it immediately before the whole forest gets infected. One such infection settled here, they call it Shturman, he and his crew set up at the sawmill, so now I don't feel safe even in my own reserve. Deal with it, it will be for the better for the forest and the people. But be careful, kid, Shturman has friends, and they all can shoot well."
  },
